{"sha": "d9fec595e83423d7c35f0457a5c6a363fdaea02d", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOmQ5ZmVjNTk1ZTgzNDIzZDdjMzVmMDQ1N2E1YzZhMzYzZmRhZWEwMmQ=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Tom Eccles", "email": "tom.eccles@codethink.co.uk", "date": "2020-07-08T20:57:57Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Tom Eccles", "email": "tom.eccles@codethink.co.uk", "date": "2020-07-08T21:02:31Z"}, "message": "ci: fix context for disabled docker images\n\nWhen the dockerfiles were moved into the host-x86_64 directory, paths\nfor COPY commands were updated with the new host-x86_64/ prefix. This\nsuggested that the intended context was src/ci/docker. However, the context\nfor disabled docker images was src/ci/docker/host-x86_64. This broke the new\npaths and prevented src/ci/docker/scripts from being included in the\ncontext at all.\n\nThis commit corrects this context allowing docker to find the files it\nneeds for COPY commands.", "tree": {"sha": "daa5d04d39bcc6800f3fb22adad9dd0d5e632ad7", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/daa5d04d39bcc6800f3fb22adad9dd0d5e632ad7"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/d9fec595e83423d7c35f0457a5c6a363fdaea02d", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/d9fec595e83423d7c35f0457a5c6a363fdaea02d", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/d9fec595e83423d7c35f0457a5c6a363fdaea02d", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/d9fec595e83423d7c35f0457a5c6a363fdaea02d/comments", "author": {"login": "tblah", "id": 3716681, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjM3MTY2ODE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3716681?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/tblah", "html_url": "https://github.com/tblah", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tblah/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tblah/following{